:

1. *Priznajem* da ne znam da li je ovo ispravan pristup. (I admit that I don't know if this is the right approach.)
2. Imao sam mnogo problema, ali *priznajem* da sam ih uspeo da rešim. (I had a lot of problems, but I admit that I managed to solve them.)
3. *Priznajući* da je to bilo teško, ipak sam uspeo da pobedim. (Admitting that it was hard, I still managed to win.)
4. *Priznajem* da sam učinio grešku i nadam se da ću biti oprošten. (I admit that I made a mistake and hope that I will be forgiven.)
5. *Priznajući* da sam malo preplašen, ipak sam otišao napred. (Admitting that I was a little scared, I still went ahead.)